results.description: The sunny days have finally come. I have been strolling with my camera in the centre of the city in Belgrade, Serbia, when a woman from the building suddenly came out with the raven on her back. Wow! With a raven! And here comes the story. Some years ago, she found him hurt on the street. She took care of him and he stayed with her, not wanting to go. He was standing on her back free, posing and showing his beautiful wings when I took a shot of him. How humans and nature have a wonderful connection. And how that connection shouldn’t be lost ever.
